<item>
            <title>[FLINK-7792] CliFrontend tests suppress logging</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/FLINK-7792</link>
                <project id="12315522" key="FLINK">Flink</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The CliFrontendTests in flink-clients call `CliFrontendTestUtils#pipeSsytemOutToNull` to suppress the various print statements.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This method however also redirects stderr, causing all log output to be suppressed as well.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
